'''Ronald Dean Verlin''' (born June 15, 1965) is an American [[college basketball]] coach and the former head coach of the men's basketball team at the [[University of the Pacific (United States)|University of the Pacific]].<ref>http://pacifictigers.com/sports/m-baskbl/2015-16/releases/20160303sp7ecj</ref> He is also the twin brother of former [[Idaho Vandals]] men's basketball coach [[Don Verlin]].<ref name="Don Verlin biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.govandals.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=17100&ATCLID=1416900/|title=Don Verlin biography|publisher=www.govandals.com|date=n.d.|accessdate=2014-12-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222063434/http://www.govandals.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=17100&ATCLID=1416900%2F|archivedate=2014-12-22|df=}}</ref>

